message.raw:
Fixed spacing in installer and load_genomedata.
Pushed #define CHUNK_NROWS to command-line option in genomedata_load_data and
provided commented-out functionality in load_genomedata.
Default CHUNK_NROWS is hard-coded into usage info, though.
Didn't see an easy way to include constant.
